name: Anchors Away! - FULLY ASSEMBLED Cupcake Mini Set
description:
A cupcake mini set with everything you need to create a cute, fun Anchors Away! cupcake display. All you need to do is provide the cupcakes!
 
12 Cupcake Wrappers (2 designs, 6 of each design).
 
12 Personalized Cupcake Toppers with lollipop sticks (each measures apprx. 2.25" in diameter). You will receive 4 of each design shown.

When purchasing, please select your child's age from the dropdown box below. If you do not see your child's age, please email me at polkadotsandlemonade@gmail.com.

Wording can be customized to fit your party! If you would like for your toppers to say something OTHER than "Happy Birthday" please leave a note or contact me at polkadotsandlemonade@gmail.com.

 Items can also be customized to fit your party theme (i.e., birthday parties, baby showers, etc.).

Other items currently available with the Anchors Away theme:

- Banner
- Favor Tags
- Water Bottle Labels
- Favor Sticker Labels
- Tented Food Labels

If you would like other coordinating items, contact me and I will design it for you!



Images from JazzyPatterns
